content:
I just noticed the single thing i have been dreaming to have is a matt. That is ridicluos i know, but I digged a little bit deeper to understand why.
Settlement. The reason i have been so focusing on the matt is that i truly wanted to settle, to have a home and the feeling that comes with it. But i couldn&rsquo;t get anyone.
Now, i actually have the money to buy a matt, a nice lovely good one. But, i resent it. I&rsquo;m not feeling well deep down and the matt (with all of the lovely feelings i imagine wih it) is totally against what my current state of mind is. I&rsquo;m in a mess, a huge fucking mess&hellip;
No matt for the wicked, eh&hellip;
